column5: Well guys I'm all packed and ready to go...... leaving around 7:00am tomorrow for deer camp  Wish me luck.... will try and get a nice report done when I get back Talk to you guys mid November  Tight lines and good luck to those who are going hunting Leechman
good luck leechman hope you bag a dandy i am hunting this weekend as well our opener here is saturday got a couple of beauties on my trail cams that i hope show up this weekend here they are
OH YEAH BABY!!  those are real nice and mature bucks    especially the last one 10 pointer  Good luck to you to rickster     Hope the big one comes back for ya
Good luck in your hunt Leechman. I won't necessarily be looking for the big one though. The smaller ones are much better table fare.
That is true Bernie.... between 2 1/2 and 3 1/2 years old are the best table fare. Got the doe tag this year and hoping to get a nice one Thanks and good luck to you
Have fun and be careful out the Jacques!!!
good luck leechman cant wait for your report
Oh you cant do that to me!!!!!!  Good luck... but DAMMITT!!!

Right on man! Heading up to the french Tomorrow morning for the whole week for deer/moose hunting as well. Couldn't sleep hardly last night too excited. Hopefully the weather is decent and i can get out in the boat for a little walleye fishing too. Good luck!

Wow Rickster those are beautiful animals.  i especially love those chocolate racks.  good luck to all going out5 next week and be safe.  Weather forecast  looks way to warm for ideal dear movement, but atleast we won't be cold in the stand.
Thats a post card if I ever seen one. Great photo there. Hey Jac,I know yer already gone,but striaght shoot,n and be safe.  Happy hunt,n.
good luck man...post your results! all is ready for me too, im out in the morning..cant wait theres still snow where im going!
Have a great time.  Looking forward to the report!
man those are some dandy bucks,  best of luck to all you all going out, gonna try to do a little stand time myself this weekend.  jason
good luck leechman....look forward to the report......
oh man 2 more weeks for me till i leave .gots a .chubby i have to get me a stealth cam...

was out yesterday and today...lotssss of females eating the carrots and apples but the 2 big bucks roaming our terittory seem to only come out once were gone and its pitch black out!!! dammit i hope he makes a mistake soon.. still 14 days of hunting to go
